step.context:
\text{The following substitution would convert}\\
I=\int\sin^3 x \cos^3 xdx \text{ to }
I=\int\dfrac{1}{2}t(t-1)dt

step.tex:
\begin{align}
I &= \int\dfrac{1}{2} t(t -1)dt = \dfrac{1}{2}\int (t^2 -t)dt\\
  &= \dfrac{1}{2}\left(\dfrac{t^3}{3}-\dfrac{t^2}{2}\right)\\
  &\text{Substituting } t = \cos^2 x \\
  &= \dfrac{1}{6}\cos ^6 x - \dfrac {1} {4} \cos^4x + C
\end{align}

\begin{align}
